>>> review*
>>>
>>> *1. Stage 0 confirmation is absent from the document header.*
>>> The Document Identity table does not record Stage 0 completion 
>>> status, the line count before and after cleaning, or TL-Dev 
>>> sign-off. The RMI module FSD correctly showed '12,198 lines cleaned 
